This is an application build on ruby 1.8.7 with ree(Ruby Enterprise Edition). This application also includes gems which are listed in Gemfile.
Using this application we can view the tweets done by any user by giving screen_name of the user and also search the tweets with the keyword in the tweets or by the date of creation of the tweet.

Note: This application is made for running on Heroku. Link to this application is : http://sharp-stone-708.heroku.com
